HEADWORD: antediluvian
<hw>an`te*di*lu"vi*an</hw>
<pr>(⟦acr⟧n`t⟦esl⟧*d⟦icr⟧*l⟦umac⟧"v⟦icr⟧*⟦ait⟧n)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
